data.description: Jingle Bells!  Jingle Bells!  Just in time for the holidays!  Recently reduced $5,000 with a seller contribution of $10,000 towards closing cost or rate buy down!  You could not ask for a better present! This stunning 6-bedroom, 5-full bathroom home with captivating brick accents, nestled in the prestigious Chapel Hill area, invites you to experience a tranquil lifestyle. Step onto the inviting brick porch, ideal for enjoying your morning coffee in the peaceful cul-de-sac setting.  Upon entering, the home exudes an open and welcoming atmosphere, cleverly designed with the steps positioned away from the front door. Discover distinct dining and living spaces, with the versatility for the living room to easily transform into a home office.  The spacious kitchen is a culinary haven, featuring a top-notch stainless steel package with a cooktop, double oven, microwave, dishwasher, and refrigerator. Enhancing the kitchen's charm are the island, wine cooler, and breakfast bar, creating a cozy ambiance that overlooks the coffered ceiling family room. Adjacent to the kitchen, a sunlit eat-in area with numerous windows leads to a serene enclosed sunroom, offering views of the expansive fenced backyard. Convenience is key, with a main floor bedroom accompanied by a full bathroom. Upstairs, each generously sized bedroom comes complete with its own full bathroom. The master bedroom and bathroom provide a personal sanctuary, boasting a sitting area with a fireplace, whirlpool tub, separate shower, double vanities, and a spacious walk-in closet. The terrace level presents the possibility of an in-law suite, equipped with a kitchenette, wet bar, bedroom featuring a trey ceiling, full bathroom, and a versatile bonus room that can serve as an exercise or craft space. A large family room offers a delightful area for family activities. Outside, a slab patio beneath the deck beckons as an excellent space for entertaining and grilling.      Don't miss the opportunity to explore this home and call it yours today!
